      "message": "My guess is that returned null is just empty method implementation provided by IDE. It should return \"this\" as in PolicyRestClient.\n\nI decided to remove return value because it was never used and can cause problems when someone decides to add additional methods to his RestClient implementations - something like\n\nmyRestClient.addRequestId(requestId).myMethod();\n\nwon't work, because addRequestId returns RestClient not MyRestClient.",
